### Installation

Source: https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth/blob/main/docs/content/docs/infrastructure/plugins/dash.mdx

Example of how to install and initialize the `dash` plugin with basic configuration parameters like API URL, KV URL, and API key.

```ts
import { betterAuth } from "better-auth";
import { dash } from "@better-auth/infra";

export const auth = betterAuth({
  plugins: [
    dash({
      apiUrl: process.env.BETTER_AUTH_API_URL,
      kvUrl: process.env.BETTER_AUTH_KV_URL,
      apiKey: process.env.BETTER_AUTH_API_KEY,
    }),
  ],
});
```

