### Basic Server Configuration with dash plugin

Source: https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth/blob/main/docs/content/docs/infrastructure/getting-started.mdx

Configuring Better Auth with the dash() plugin.

```ts
import { betterAuth } from "better-auth";
import { dash } from "@better-auth/infra"; // [!code highlight]

export const auth = betterAuth({
  // ... your existing Better Auth config
  plugins: [
    dash({ // [!code highlight]
      apiKey: process.env.BETTER_AUTH_API_KEY, // [!code highlight]
    }), // [!code highlight]
  ],
});
```

