### Basic Client Configuration

Source: https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth/blob/main/docs/content/docs/infrastructure/getting-started.mdx

Configuring the Better Auth client with dashClient() and sentinelClient() plugins.

```ts
import { createAuthClient } from "better-auth/client";
import { dashClient, sentinelClient } from "@better-auth/infra/client";

export const authClient = createAuthClient({
  plugins: [
    dashClient(),
    sentinelClient({
      autoSolveChallenge: true, // Automatically solve PoW challenges
    }),
  ],
});
```

