## Configure tsconfig 


    Configure the `tsconfig.json` file to include `strict` mode.

    For this demo, we have also changed the import alias from `~` to `@` and set it to the `src` directory.

    ```json title="tsconfig.json"
    {
        "compilerOptions": {
            "paths": {
                "@/_": [
                    "./src/_"
                ]
            },
            "strict": true,
            "baseUrl": "."
        }
    }
    ```

